obvious.impl
Class DataFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
  obvious.data.DataFactory
      obvious.impl.DataFactoryImpl

public class DataFactoryImpl
extends DataFactory

Implements abstract class DataFactory for the Obvious Impl implementation. This the default data factory for Obvious, used when no other has been specified. Thus, it should be used in other goals than testing.

Author:
Pierre-Luc Hémery
